&lt;h1&gt;Sample Welcome Message&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;span class=red&gt; This is a sample welcome message that you can edit as you see fit in order for you to introduce your e-portfolio to your class. &lt;/span&gt; This Bedford e-Portfolio gives you a single place to collect and reflect on your work. You can compose directly in your e-Portfolio or upload word documents, video, audio, or images that best represent who you are and what you have created. Just click on the e-Portfolio tab at the top of the page and get started!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
